gracias!

Until now I hadn't heard Che Sedaka. I got Trippie Town yesterday and love it! I'm going to DL and seed it and Alerta Bizhota. Thank you! 


How come the third Che album you have up here is 4 gigs? Is it more then one album?
Yes, it also includes a DVD, with live sessions and interviews.
I saw these guys at Sunfest 2009 in London Ont Can. They were amazing, bought 2 cd's and looking to find more of their music online. Thanks for posting this wonderful group.
